On U.S. support for Osama bin Laden specifically, and for its sponsorship of international terrorism in general, see Phil Gasper's "<a href="http://www.isreview.org/issues/20/CIA_binladen_afghan.shtml" target="_blank">Afghanistan, the CIA, Bin Laden and the Taliban</a>" and Katherine Dwyer's <a href="http://www.isreview.org/issues/20/rogue_state.shtml" target="_blank">"Rogue State: A History of U.S. Terror."</a><p>

